    "asOf": "2020-08-14",
    "date": "2020-11-17T15:24:33Z",
    "text": "Supporting Early-Career Researchers Act\n\nThis bill authorizes the National Science Foundation to establish a two-year pilot program to award grants to highly qualified early-career investigators to carry out an independent research program at the institution of higher education chosen by such investigator, to last for a period not greater than two years."
